attributes.text: Turn right on Portage Ave (TC-1 W)
Take the exit on the right to merge onto TC-101 S / Perimeter Hwy
Take the exit on the right to merge onto MB-3
Make a U-turn and go back on Provincial Trunk Highway 3 (MB-3)
Take the exit on the right to merge onto Perimeter Hwy (TC-100 E)
Take exit 18A on the right to merge onto Pembina Hwy / City Rte-42 N
Finish at Location 2, on the left
